## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **ropeginterferon alfa-2b Besremi 2021** = first FDA disease-modifying PV — paradigm shift. PROUD-PV + CONTINUATION-PV trial 데이터 = JAK2 V617F allele burden 만성 reduction + molecular response. pegylated 2-week dosing → 4-week dosing. 50+ year hydroxyurea cytoreduction-only era 종료. quantum-VQE 의 IFN-AR1/2 + pegylation linker fit (cross-bone_marrow_failure).
2. **ruxolitinib Jakafi 2014 PV approval** = JAK1/2 inhibitor — PV second-line hydroxyurea-resistant/intolerant. RESPONSE + RESPONSE-2 trial. ET research MAJIC-ET 만성 hydroxyurea-resistant. quantum-VQE JAK2 V617F + JH1 kinase domain pocket fit (cross-myelofibrosis_specific).
3. **JAK2 V617F (Vainchenker 2005) + CALR exon 9 (Klampfl + Nangalia 2013) + MPL W515L (Pikman 2006)** = MPN driver mutation triad. 95% PV + 50% ET JAK2 + 30% ET CALR + 5% ET MPL. quantum-VQE 의 driver mutation pocket selectivity 직접 fit.
4. **hydroxyurea (Hydrea 1967) 50+ year backbone** = 만성 1L cytoreduction PV/ET high-risk. ribonucleotide reductase inhibition. leukemogenic 만성 long-term issue 논쟁 (PT-1 trial). quantum-VQE 의 ribonucleotide reductase pocket leverage.
5. **anagrelide Agrylin 1997** = ET 1차 platelet reduction selective megakaryocyte. PT-1 trial = anagrelide + aspirin vs hydroxyurea + aspirin → hydroxyurea 우월 (특히 JAK2+). quantum-VQE PDE3 + platelet selectivity fit.
6. **bomedemstat IMG-7289 Imago Bio LSD1 inhibitor** = research ET + MF Phase 3 IMPACT-MF + ET. LSD1 (KDM1A) histone demethylase epigenetic. 2024 Merck $1.35B 인수 (cross-myelofibrosis_specific + bone_marrow_failure). quantum-VQE 의 LSD1 FAD-binding pocket leverage.
7. **INCA033989 first CALR-mutant selective antibody** = research ET + MF — Incyte. CALR exon 9 mutant 의 neoepitope 표적. 만성 disease-modifying 가능성. wild-type CALR sparing. quantum-VQE 의 CALR-mutant epitope + Fab geometry fit (cross-myelofibrosis_specific).
8. **IFN-α (recombinant 1986) + pegylated IFN (PEGASYS 2002 HCV) → ropeginterferon Besremi 2021** = IFN era 35+ year evolution. recombinant → pegylated → ropeginterferon. PROUD-PV (vs hydroxyurea) + CONTINUATION-PV. molecular response + JAK2 allele burden reduction = first disease-modifying PV.
9. **transformation risk (PV → MF 10-15% 15년 + AML 2-5% + ET → MF 5-10% + AML 1-2%)** = MPN clonal evolution 만성. 만성 + 만성 + 만성 long-term morbidity (cross-myelofibrosis_specific + aml_specific). hydroxyurea + busulfan + 32P leukemogenic 논쟁. ropeginterferon = leukemogenic risk 없음 신호.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, PV/ET 임상 의미 한정. 한국 K-PV/ET 식약처 framework + 산정특례 administrative lens 한정.

